modshell:Command-driven scriptable Modbus utility
modshell:
modshell:This is a utility that can be used on several
modshell:operating systems, which can communicate with
modshell:connected equipment using Modbus/ASCII, -/RTU
modshell:and -/TCP protocols. The program can - even
modshell:automatically - read, write or copy data from
modshell:one device to another (e.g. transferring
modshell:settings).
